例句: We live in the digital age now.
翻译: 我们现在生活在数字时代。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/word-images/age_1778232737991_a66fe45f.png?sign=1780824738-80a66cd6f1-0-b644baf2764a87d69464cef99f1fdf693d24a9dbadc75af6b71589bd9dab33ea', null), ('86', 'accent', '/ˈæksent/', '口音(n)；重音(c)；着重点(sing)；强调(vt)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'She has a British accent.', null, '她有一口英国口音。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/word-images/accent_1778232757963_44f0568f.png?sign=1780824758-10d3a2417a-0-458d523e45206358941fd7266f6ddc7be98632bdaaa6d3fecbed137487e2b38c', null), ('87', 'tone', '/toʊn/', '语气(c)；音调；色调(n)；(活动)基调(u, sing)；给…定调子(vt)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'She changed her tone suddenly.', null, '她突然改变了语气。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/word-images/tone_1778232790553_392560f9.png?sign=1780824791-a5d650e24b-0-561840d0db8d9cb5b79118192b450c7180c8257cedd03d00b918a54fd75d1a36', null), ('88', 'voice', '/vɔɪs/', '(说话等的)声音、嗓音(n)；意见(c)；发言权(u, sing)；表达(vt)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'She raised her voice in the meeting.', null, '她在会议上提高了嗓门。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/word-images/voice_1778232814170_26125bc3.png?sign=1780824814-5220ccb8dc-0-349cf8365fd67a764ad2b41eb5b60e6c221d75f0f972d3e39fef343f21db3fb0', null), ('89', 'mind', '/maɪnd/', '心、头脑(n)；心思；记忆力(c)；介意(~ doing)；注意、当心(v)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'She minds her mind when reading.', null, '她阅读时留意自己的心思。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/word-images/mind_1778232841647_74aee5b5.png?sign=1780824842-441cbdc7eb-0-98f6be8ef719c236c7eda6cb8cdfe5a5a848d8b39bcc4a768e47ae6e29ace18b', null), ('90', 'soul', '/soʊl/', '灵魂、心灵(c)；精神、精髓(u)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'Her soul feels peaceful now.', null, '她的心灵此刻感到平静。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/word-images/soul_1778232863297_65bedcc5.png?sign=1780824864-f1009ea617-0-05dc8b48a220d104b578c1d09c9b14511b6eb64fc6ce145cd25d673139cca73e', null), ('91', 'spirit', '/ˈspɪrɪt/', '精神、心灵(n)；情绪(pl)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'Her spirit lifts when friends visit.', null, '朋友来访时她情绪高涨。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/word-images/spirit_1778232893854_c7216e68.png?sign=1780824894-e3b23754c8-0-a5ddb6313fda791a35c292a4d032c2b3788a7c139ab49e27eada178a59f75ba5', null), ('92', 'conscience', '/ˈkɑːnʃəns/', '良心；愧疚(n)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'He had a clear conscience about the decision.', null, '对这个决定他问心无愧。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/image/generate_image_a9a2c15e-1d9d-4ca4-b5b7-0d6ed481d885.jpeg?sign=1808469407-2c7e5726c6-0-3682cfb1dae73d38126dcbafa2c5974c4344f704d892a198b076aea2bf63f54b', null), ('93', 'ego', '/ˈiːɡoʊ/', '自我；自负、自自尊心(c)(pl, egos)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'He has a fragile ego and needs encouragement.', null, '他自尊心脆弱，需要鼓励。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/image/generate_image_273e80e1-e827-4442-8e46-650524507ec4.jpeg?sign=1808469430-91d62c5762-0-9adaa0ae1c85b0bb90a6a3be15ee51391733eef4570ac24ffee419495e6137b2', null), ('94', 'beauty', '/ˈbjuːti/', '美、美丽(u)；美人、美好的物(c)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'She is known for her beauty and grace.', null, '她以美丽和优雅著称。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/image/generate_image_0a95e73b-c259-442b-a8ba-ee9e91b2a140.jpeg?sign=1808469351-3b3be2e6a4-0-908ccf41db65b86c4a3a6784ddb80a63fac2ba32c1cb43d9df464256f3275439', null), ('95', 'grace', '/ɡreɪs/', '(动作的)优雅、优美；(上帝的)恩典(u)；使(某地或某物)优美(vt)', '2026-04-21 20:04:00.209556', 'She moved with grace and elegance.', null, '她举止优雅得体。', 'https://coze-coding-project.tos.coze.site/coze_storage_7630677478465568811/image/generate_image_bfc13f3f-67a9-4a2f-b3f9-648149638a62.jpeg?sign=1808469527-3c2baf303c-0-faec83072ee8d67fa9811ffef39e19d062c40a6a09187